<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT49">
<l>malaiyāmai mēlvaittu vācukiyaic cuṟṟi</l>
<l>talaiyāmai tāṉorukai paṟṟi yalaiyāmaṟ</l>
<l>pīṟak kaṭainta perumāṉ tiruṉāmaṅ</l>
<l>kūṟuvatē yāvarkkuṅ kūṟṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[May] the uttering of the sacred names---</l>
<l rend="indent">of the Lord who churned [the ocean] so that [the nectar] burst [through]</l>
<l rend="indent">placing the mountain on the Tortoise and</l>
<l rend="indent">tying Vāsuki around [it],</l>
<l rend="indent">The Tortoise itself holding on to [its] top, with one hand,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [the water] does not shake---</l>
<l>Be the speech for everyone.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
